There will be mailing list for xblast announces.  It will cover
announces of new "official" xblast releases. We can also use
it announce other xblast resources on Internet, i.e
websites, new level files.

If you want to subscribe to this mailing list send a mail to
vogel@ikp.uni-koeln.de with the subject "xblast subscribe".

To unsubscribe from the mailing list send a mail to
vogel@ikp.uni-koeln.de with the subject "xblast unsubscribe".



If enough people are interested I will also try to setup a mailing
list for xblast discussions.

